character <PERSON> Remi </PERSON> <PERSON> Boncoeur </PERSON> in `` On the <LOCATION> Road </LOCATION>.'' `` When <PERSON> Jack </PERSON> and I were sitting around <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION> talking of going to sea, we dreamed of a lot of things,'' he said. `` But there was nothing like this.''
