<HEAD>Self-Styled Electronics Expert Held by Feds Because Sharpton Tapes
are Blank</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MITCHELL LANDSBERG</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
